[SPEAKER_00]: it takes some of the cars off the road.

350
00:32:38,192 --> 00:32:41,574
[SPEAKER_00]: And the more bikes there are, the more safe it is for bicyclists.

351
00:32:42,415 --> 00:32:46,437
[SPEAKER_00]: If you're the only bike, it's much more dangerous than if there are like a lot of bikes.

352
00:32:47,298 --> 00:32:51,761
[SPEAKER_00]: So there actually is a lot of room for educating residents.

