376
00:34:49,152 --> 00:35:00,278
[SPEAKER_00]: And we want to turn it into commercial and residential and stuff that actually benefits the city and provides taxes and income for the city and benefits to the community.

377
00:35:01,445 --> 00:35:09,269
[SPEAKER_00]: So one of the questions has been, well, then where would we put an electric bus depot in this area, basically north of Boston?

378
00:35:09,289 --> 00:35:11,550
[SPEAKER_00]: Because that's where they've been planning to put one.

379
00:35:12,770 --> 00:35:16,352
