[SPEAKER_00]: They don't wanna work for, although I will say, and I just have to be clear, I am also seeing individuals who are saying, I had soul searching and I don't wanna be doing corporate work anymore.

748
01:14:41,291 --> 01:14:44,613
[SPEAKER_00]: And I wanna be doing something where I can make a real difference and change.

749
01:14:45,353 --> 01:14:46,814
[SPEAKER_00]: And we've benefited from that.

750
01:14:48,295 --> 01:14:51,978
[SPEAKER_00]: I have one staff in my office who in fact did exactly that.

751
01:14:52,158 --> 01:14:54,500
[SPEAKER_00]: And we are very happy that she much prefers

752
01:14:55,060 --> 01:15:03,306
[SPEAKER_00]: to be doing public service than, there's a reason they call it public service, which by the way, sounds like volunteering, but it's actually your career.

753
01:15:03,326 --> 01:15:16,576
[SPEAKER_00]: But I've talked to a couple of people, but it's like a trickle of people who are saying, actually, what I wanna do is do good for my community.

754
01:15:17,136 --> 01:15:21,860
[SPEAKER_00]: And you're seeing a flood of people who are like, I'm gonna go to industry and make real money.

