01:16:24,767 --> 01:16:30,649
[SPEAKER_00]: The positions that are open that are very hard to fill right now, I have economic development director.

765
01:16:31,467 --> 01:16:41,792
[SPEAKER_00]: I had somebody apply straight out of college, and I'm sorry, but you do not have the experience to be our economic development director straight out of college.

766
01:16:41,952 --> 01:16:55,979
[SPEAKER_00]: For our housing planner positions, we wanted three to five years of experience and knowledge of Massachusetts housing programs, but we are now reevaluating whether we should consider straight out of college applicants.

767
01:16:58,722 --> 01:17:02,764
[SPEAKER_00]: Some of the other positions open in the city are assessor and city solicitor.

768
01:17:03,204 --> 01:17:13,870
