857
01:25:35,838 --> 01:25:45,182
[SPEAKER_02]: The issue is some of the rebates from the Inflation Reduction Act aren't in effect yet until the state sets it up.

858
01:25:45,482 --> 01:25:45,602
[SPEAKER_02]: So

859
01:25:46,653 --> 01:25:55,294
[SPEAKER_02]: It's almost better to procrastinate a little bit in order to get the rebate from the feds because it isn't available yet.

