861
01:26:09,337 --> 01:26:15,458
[SPEAKER_02]: You're paying a lot more, especially in colder weather than natural gas, unfortunately.

862
01:26:17,016 --> 01:26:31,922
[SPEAKER_02]: There were a couple of plots in the presentation that show how it's very interesting to compare the cost of a heat pump system in winter, depending on the price of electricity.

863
01:26:32,062 --> 01:26:38,985
[SPEAKER_02]: And with current rates, you're paying more than natural gas heating.

864
01:26:40,585 --> 01:26:43,646
