866
01:26:46,142 --> 01:26:49,947
[SPEAKER_02]: It's, it's not good for electricity, it's winter.

867
01:26:50,908 --> 01:26:54,332
[SPEAKER_02]: Even, even though natural gas has gone up, electricity has gone up even more.

868
01:26:57,957 --> 01:27:02,723
[SPEAKER_06]: I find it curious that natural gas went up because, you know, much of our natural gas comes from

869
01:27:04,300 --> 01:27:09,921
