893
01:29:48,134 --> 01:29:53,155
[SPEAKER_00]: And he got wildly different quotes with wildly different suggestions about what we should do.

894
01:29:53,695 --> 01:30:10,358
[SPEAKER_00]: And so the one thing that he pulled out of there is he said, I wanna know more about this hiring Abode Energy through Green Energy Consumer Alliance to give me like neutral advice on what's going on here and which of these things makes the most sense.

895
01:30:11,069 --> 01:30:15,933
[SPEAKER_00]: and honestly, to learn more about some of the incentives that aren't readily available yet.

896
01:30:17,013 --> 01:30:31,504
