897
01:30:33,987 --> 01:30:52,555
[SPEAKER_03]: I think it is that in Cambridge, and I think in Brooklyn as well, the city has hired counselors, advisors, whatever, and homeowners can get an hour or two of basically free advice, which presumably is not being affected by anybody putting anything in their pocket.

898
01:30:52,935 --> 01:30:54,976
[SPEAKER_03]: But it is an extremely frustrating process.

899
01:30:57,706 --> 01:31:05,991
[SPEAKER_05]: And I have to say that even if the party you're dealing with is not trying to sell you something, which is rarely the case.

900
01:31:08,132 --> 01:31:10,674
[SPEAKER_05]: Each house is different.

901
01:31:11,855 --> 01:31:15,517
[SPEAKER_05]: Each system is that's already there is different.

902
01:31:16,357 --> 01:31:24,062
[SPEAKER_05]: If my boiler was bought less than five years ago, it's a different equation than your boiler that was bought 20 years ago.

903
01:31:24,946 --> 01:31:28,928
[SPEAKER_05]: that you'd be replacing.

904
01:31:28,948 --> 01:31:47,337
[SPEAKER_05]: And people have said, well, you just have to put a lot of solar panels on your roof to reduce your, by the time they tell you all the things they want you to do to reduce your fuel use, I'm saying, well, why wouldn't I just do those things and not change my fuel system out?

905
01:31:49,090 --> 01:31:53,773
[SPEAKER_05]: So it's like any other home remodeling project.

906
01:31:53,934 --> 01:31:58,016
[SPEAKER_05]: It's not off the shelf, and it's not one size fits all.

907
01:31:58,077 --> 01:32:02,540
