01:32:20,564 --> 01:32:23,445
[SPEAKER_10]: This is a complicated process for my own house.

914
01:32:24,025 --> 01:32:28,347
[SPEAKER_10]: It took me as an expert in architecture and in energy

915
01:32:29,167 --> 01:32:30,688
[SPEAKER_10]: a ton of time.

916
01:32:30,708 --> 01:32:37,951
[SPEAKER_10]: And I am definitely paying more than I would have with gas, I am paying about the same as I was with oil.

917
01:32:37,971 --> 01:32:42,353
[SPEAKER_10]: And that was after a very substantial renovation.

918
01:32:43,874 --> 01:32:50,357
[SPEAKER_10]: So paying a lot in order to pay the same amount is not really an equation that most people would go through.

919
01:32:50,377 --> 01:32:51,998
[SPEAKER_10]: So it

